notes: Two things you'll never forget about Tommie Shurtleff: he is witty and courteous. Of course he's also caring, humble and discreet, but those are often overshadowed by tendencies of being deceitful as well. His wit though, this is what he is so well-liked for. Friends usually count on this and his heroic nature especially when they need comforting or support.
